title: BRIEF-Univision Engineering FY rev down 24 pct
text:
Sept 10 Univision Engineering Ltd
* Fy net pretax profit from continuing operations 130,000 stg versus 3 million stg year ago
* Fy revenue fell 24.2 percent to 6.7 million stg
* Final dividend 0.034 penceper share Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Bengaluru Newsroom: +91 80 6749 1136)
